sequenceDiagram
  actor User
  participant UI as React UI
  participant API as Local API
  participant Store as SQLite KB Store
  participant AI as AI Package

  User->>UI: open http://localhost:5173
  UI->>API: GET /api/kbs
  API->>Store: listKnowledgeBases()
  Store-->>API: KB summaries
  API-->>UI: KB list
  UI->>API: GET /api/kbs/:kb and /repos
  API->>Store: load graph and repo overviews
  Store-->>API: graph, freshness, doc metadata
  API-->>UI: render graph, repo list, docs list

  User->>UI: click repo/service/endpoint
  UI->>API: GET doc endpoint
  API->>Store: load cached Markdown doc
  Store-->>API: LLM + deterministic variants
  API-->>UI: render selected variant

  User->>UI: click Regenerate
  UI->>API: POST regenerate endpoint
  API->>Store: build graph evidence
  API->>AI: generate docs
  AI-->>API: new cached doc
  API->>Store: save doc
  API-->>UI: render new doc
